    bibo:volume "4061" ;
    dc:creator "Chang, Liang; Sun, Xin" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of Allonychiurus Yoshii, 1995 (Collembola, Onychiuridae) from eastern China, with a key to world species of the genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270400>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270401> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270400>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Allonychiurus zhejiangensis sp. nov. 1, dorsal chaetotaxy; 2, labrum; 3, PAO and anterior cephalic pso; 4, maxillary palp; 5, labium; 6, antenna; 7, sensory clubs on Ant. III sensory organ; 8, ventral side of Abd. I – VI;. Scales: 0.1 mm (1, 6, 8), 0.01 mm (2 – 5, 7)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/270400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.270401>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 17. Allonychiurus zhejiangensis sp. nov. 9, ventral side of head; 10, right part of head; 11, right side of Th. II tergum; 12, right part of Abd. IV tergum; 13, distal part of leg I; 14, distal part of leg III; 15, central part of abdominal sternum III; 16, central part of abdominal sternum IV; 17, anal valves. Scales: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/270401/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

